creator: Ella Wheeler Wilcox
description:
LibriVox recording of The Kingdom of Love by Ella Wheeler Wilcox.
Read in English by Michele Fry; Diana Schmidt; Newgatenovelist; Sonia; Leonard Wilson; Greg Giordano; Jacquelyn Bengfort; Ian; Mary Myers; Peter Yearsley; Jude; Jennifer Fournier
This is a volume of poetry by Ella Wheeler Wilcox, named after the poem 'the Kingdom of Love'. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
